# Weed and Read — Project Context

- **Business:** Privacy-first cannabis boutique in Albuquerque, New Mexico.
- **Vibe:** Victorian bank reading room (dark mahogany, gold trim, warm parchment, vintage books) juxtaposed with a modest blue and green storefront.
- **Audience:** Older, literary-minded patrons who value extreme privacy and quiet over loud modern dispensary culture.
- **Stack:** React, Tailwind CSS, Node.js, Prisma, and raw SQL.

Prefer library/reading-room metaphors over typical dispensary language and visuals.
